Privacy standards
You have complete ownership and control over your content and account, and can decide how much of your data you share with others. It is your responsibility to verify the identity of anyone you invite to your account and monitor their access and use of your account and data. We are not liable for any unauthorized access or use of your account or data by anyone you have authorized. As required by GDPR, we will disclose the personal data we collect and process about you, as well as the purposes for which we use that data, in this Privacy Notice.
