Deleting your account
Once you create an account with us, it will remain active until you or we delete it. You can terminate your account and stop using the app at any time. If you choose to delete your account only, your recipe data will remain in our system and we will retain ownership rights to that content. Alternatively, you can delete your account and all data you have created in the app by selecting the ‘delete account and data’ option. We reserve the right to suspend or delete your account for reasons including but not limited to, lack of use, violation of this Privacy Policy or our Terms and Conditions, or other reasons which we deem sufficient in our discretion. Please note that once you delete Your Data, it cannot be recovered. If you have given access to Your Data to third parties for analytical or other purposes in both anonymous and/or personally identified formats, and have agreed that some or all of Your Data will not be deleted in the future, then Your Data will continue to be stored, shared, and used as you have consented.
Children’s Privacy
This website is intended for use by individuals who are 13 years of age or older, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under 13 years of age. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child under 13 without obtaining parental consent, we will take immediate steps to delete that information from our servers. If you are a parent or legal guardian and believe that we might have collected information from your child without your consent, please contact us immediately so that we can take appropriate action.
